event.name: SYS_SERVER_CERTIFICATE_OK
event.description: Generated when threshold check is rearmed for specific data collection item. Parameters: dciName - Parameter name dciDescription - Item description dciId - Data collection item ID instance - Instance thresholdValue - Threshold value currentValue - Actual value dciValue - Current DCI value
event.message: Server certificate for tunnel connections was renewed, has now %<{multipliers, units}currentValue> left

event.name: DC_SERVER_THREAD_POOL_TOO_BUSY
event.description: Generated by server thread pool load average threshold
event.message: Load average for server thread pool %<instance> is too high (%<{multipliers, units}currentValue>)

event.name: SYS_SERVER_CERTIFICATE_EXPIRING
event.description: Custom data collection threshold event. Parameters: dciName - Parameter name dciDescription - Item description thresholdValue - Threshold value currentValue - Actual value dciId - Data collection item ID instance - Instance isRepeatedEvent - Repeat flag dciValue - Current DCI value
event.message: Server certificate for tunnel connections is expiring, %<{multipliers, units}currentValue> left
